püren. Anliegen ist, für die Implikationen von Begriffen und Narrativen zu sensibilisieren und Dialoge zwischen Disziplinen anzuregen.  aConcepts such as (forced) migration, displacement, asylum, and diaspora describe phenomena that are also negotiated in exile studies. This volume brings together interdisciplinary contributions that trace their common features but also the different connotations and contexts that they evoke. The aim is to make readers aware of the implications of concepts and narratives, and to encourage dialogue between disciplines.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 4aAsyl. 4aFlucht. 4aMigration. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aAlkin, Ömer, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBandau, Anja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBannasch, Bettina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBannasch, Bettina, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBauer, Fabian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBavendamm, Gundula, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBischoff, Doerte, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBischoff, Doerte, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBodenheimer, Alfred, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChihaia, Matei, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDavies, Steffan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDogramaci, Burcu, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDogramaci, Burcu, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEigler, Friederike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vo